Script for creating gz release packages.

Requires:
- Tools to build gz and homeboy
- git
- unzip
- gzip or xz for creating linux releases
- zip or 7zip for creating windows releases
- genisoimage, or hfsprogs with guestmount or sudo for mounting hfs images for
  creating macos releases on linux, optionally with dmg from libdmg-hfsplus for
  compression.

See ./gz-release for usage.
